library(SubscaleExplorer)
library(psych)
Data <- read.csv("~/Data.txt", sep="")
getscale(Data, "reference.xlsx", column="Subscales")

a<-unlist(output)
a<-data.frame((vapply(output,unlist,unlist(output[[1]]))))

for(i in 1:ncol(a)){
  assign(names(output)[i], a[[i]])
}
